name: What Dutch People Eat - Episode 1
description:
What do Dutch people eat?  Lots of strange stuff but it's all delicious.  So join me for a journey through some Dutch treats from chips with mayonnaise through to biscuit sandwiches and the famous stroopwafels.   

Food in Holland  - video features poffertjes, oliebollen, vlaai, patat, hagelslag, apple tart, drop and much more.
